item.title: HackTheBox - Mailroom
item.description: Writeup for HackTheBox’s Mailroom machine. Starting off with the nmap scan, we can see that port 80 and 22 is open: PORT STATE SERVICE REASON VERSION 22/tcp open ssh syn-ack OpenSSH 8.
